reviewText: Enjoyed this movie. Very well done.
Too boring. I have never made it past the 20 min mark. For blu, the vid is low quality too.

The blu-ray version of " Carrier " is very entertaining but with one problem, it's way too short when compared with the dvd version titled " Carrier ". This blu-ray version is only 90 Mins long and the dvd version is more than 10 hours.
